Class GreenRoomBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.Controller.Data.RoomBuilders.Map4Rooms.GreenRoomBuilder

  • public class GreenRoomBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an example for the builder of a room. Every room is represented by an CopyOnWriteArrayList of cells, and it has a colour as an identifier.
